name: Animalia Paradoxa
tagline: The contradictory creatures of data analytics
body:
This is a list of data analytics resources that I've compiled over the 18 months. It contains software projects, books, articles, blog posts, and presentations. And one email.

This is not (even close to) an exhaustive list on the topic of data analytics. It's just a list of the items I've found most helpful or interesting so far.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
